Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.55,0:01:26.59,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}悄然隱匿的 我心如陷阱與炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.91,0:01:31.89,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊啊啊 脫離成群的視線
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.11,0:01:32.93,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}倖存者會是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.93,0:01:35.15,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}勝負僅此一回
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.53,0:01:38.25,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}此刻 點燃烈火
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.69,0:01:45.71,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一步步地逼近 我所追求的更多賜予
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.39,0:01:49.69,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在被他人盜走前 你看 愛在燃燒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.69,0:01:51.95,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感觸到了熱氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.19,0:01:57.13,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}火辣辣的 刺激的浪漫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.07,0:01:57.13,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an9\pos(1890, 180)\blur3\fs30}去感受它 去感受它 去感受它
